{"tid":2034621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警察隊員佐級協會形容現時是「黎明前的黑暗」","createTime":"2020-05-25T10:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T01:32:17.000Z","uid":20933,"like":13,"dislike":622,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"42c043fb8311865fcce79048e65097516979c596","tid":2034621,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:34:32.000Z","msg":"昨日有網民發起反對港區國安法的遊行，引發警民衝突。警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉去信協會會員，形容現時是「黎明前的黑暗」，他相信如今黑暗真正走到盡頭，光明即將照亮前路。<br />\n<br />\n對於昨日有警員和途人受傷，他譴責暴徒的違法行為，以及在背後推波助瀾的「縱暴份子」，指他們的作為是與民為敵，甚至直接威脅他人生命安全，警方必定會嚴正執法。<br />\n<br />\n林志偉又質疑，市民再次要為暴徒的暴力和破壞「埋單」，指涉事地方大部份商業活動被迫停止，批評有暴徒完全漠視市民飯碗和生計，又指市民對經濟復甦及正常生活的期待，被少部分人虛無飄緲的政治訴求凌駕。"},{"pid":"d9e8fd9f1ed88d83172c7c2c009baebddcee5b98","tid":2034621,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:34:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290050&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1290050%26csid%3D261_341&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3pLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=e8bf134a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290050&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"bdaaee4e38c409111d41115b0c914fa875233d75","tid":2034621,"uid":129169,"like":94,"dislike":2,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:35:25.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abc717368c03e9573aa41b47d9a16fe429faec2","tid":2034621,"uid":48083,"like":627,"dislike":1,"score":626,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"成日抄人口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8139f12dd2cfa62a23b8214f428d07fb30b4d1ef","tid":2034621,"uid":259812,"like":318,"dislike":0,"score":318,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05